Quel est l'évolution YTD du ca souscription  au mois de Mars

Requête SQL envoyée :

WITH current_year_data AS (
    SELECT 
        year,
        month,
        (SUM(ca_data) + SUM(ca_voix)) AS total_ca
    FROM 
        monthly_souscription
    WHERE 
        year = (SELECT MAX(year) FROM monthly_souscription)
        AND month <= 3
    GROUP BY 
        year, month
),
previous_year_data AS (
    SELECT 
        year,
        month,
        (SUM(ca_data) + SUM(ca_voix)) AS total_ca
    FROM 
        monthly_souscription
    WHERE 
        year = (SELECT MAX(year) - 1 FROM monthly_souscription)
        AND month <= 3
    GROUP BY 
        year, month
),
total_comparison AS (
    SELECT 
        current.year AS current_year,
        current.month AS current_month,
        previous.year AS previous_year,
        (current.total_ca - previous.total_ca) / previous.total_ca * 100 AS ytd_growth_percentage
    FROM 
        current_year_data current
    JOIN 
        previous_year_data previous 
    ON 
        current.month = previous.month
)
SELECT 
    current_year,
    current_month,
    previous_year,
    ytd_growth_percentage
FROM 
    total_comparison
ORDER BY 
    current_year DESC, current_month DESC;

Segmenter les utilisateurs par profils marketing, zones géographiques et formules tarifaires

Requête SQL envoyée :

SELECT 
    rdcpx.year AS year,
    rdcpx.month AS month,
    rdcpx.segment_marche AS marketing_profile,
    COALESCE(rsi.region_90j, rpm.region_90j) AS region,
    COALESCE(rsi.departement_90j, rpm.departement_90j) AS department,
    COALESCE(rdcpx.formule_xarre, rsi.formule_dmgp, rpm.formule_dmgp) AS tariff_plan
FROM 
    reporting_daily_ca_pag_xarre AS rdcpx
LEFT JOIN 
    reporting_sargal_inscrits AS rsi ON rdcpx.segment_marche = rsi.segment_marche AND rdcpx.formule_xarre = rsi.formule_dmgp
LEFT JOIN 
    reporting_parc_monthly AS rpm ON rdcpx.segment_marche = rpm.segment_marche AND rdcpx.formule_xarre = rpm.formule_dmgp
WHERE 
    rdcpx.year = 2025
ORDER BY 
    rdcpx.year DESC, rdcpx.month DESC;
Donne-moi le nombre d’abonnés ayant souscrit à ILLIMIX JOUR 500F sur les 3 derniers mois

Requête SQL envoyée :

SELECT 
    ds.year AS year,
    ds.month AS month,
    COUNT(DISTINCT ds.msisdn) AS nombre_abonnes
FROM 
    daily_souscription AS ds
WHERE 
    ds.offer_name LIKE '%ILLIMIX JOUR 500F%' 
    AND CONCAT(CAST(ds.year AS STRING), LPAD(CAST(ds.month AS STRING), 2, '0')) >= CONCAT(CAST(YEAR(CURRENT_DATE - INTERVAL 3 MONTH) AS STRING), LPAD(CAST(MONTH(CURRENT_DATE - INTERVAL 3 MONTH) AS STRING), 2, '0'))
GROUP BY 
    ds.year, ds.month
ORDER BY 
    ds.year DESC, ds.month DESC;

SELECT 
    data_usage.year AS year,
    data_usage.month AS month,
    data_usage.client_id,

        WHEN SUM(data_usage.total_volume) >= 1000 THEN 'Actif Régulier'
        WHEN SUM(data_usage.total_volume) BETWEEN 100 AND 999 THEN 'Occasionnel'

    END AS usage_segment

    data_usage.client_id
ORDER BY

Requête SQL envoyée :

-- Suppose there is a table `communes_drv_mapping` that maps communes to DRV
-- with columns: commune (commune name) and drv (DRV name)

SELECT 
    rc.year AS year,
    rc.month AS month,
    cd.drv AS drv,
    SUM(rc.ca_recharges) AS total_ca_recharges
FROM 
    reporting_ca_monthly AS rc
JOIN 
    communes_drv_mapping AS cd ON rc.ca_cr_commune = cd.commune
WHERE 
    cd.drv LIKE '%SUD%' OR
    cd.drv LIKE '%CENTRE%' OR
    cd.drv LIKE '%DAKAR%' OR
    cd.drv LIKE '%NORD%' OR
    cd.drv LIKE '%EST%' OR
    cd.drv LIKE '%Roaming%' OR
    cd.drv LIKE '%Autres%'
GROUP BY 
    rc.year, rc.month, cd.drv
ORDER BY 
    rc.year DESC, rc.month DESC, total_ca_recharges DESC;

quel est lévolution Year To Date de la pénétration des échangeurs Sargal au mois de Mars

Requête SQL envoyée :

SELECT 
    current_data.year as year,
    current_data.month as month,
    SUM(current_data.nb_j_distinct) as total_days_current_year,
    SUM(previous_data.nb_j_distinct) as total_days_previous_year,
    (SUM(current_data.nb_j_distinct) - SUM(previous_data.nb_j_distinct)) / SUM(previous_data.nb_j_distinct) * 100 as ytd_growth_percentage
FROM 
    daily_parc_sargal as current_data
LEFT JOIN 
    daily_parc_sargal as previous_data
ON 
    current_data.month = previous_data.month 
    AND current_data.day = previous_data.day
    AND current_data.year = previous_data.year + 1
WHERE 
    current_data.month <= 3
    AND current_data.year = (SELECT MAX(year) FROM daily_parc_sargal)
GROUP BY 
    current_data.year, current_data.month
ORDER BY 
    current_data.year DESC, current_data.month DESC;
